Class FixedHistogramDataModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.base.node.viz.histogram.datamodel.FixedHistogramDataModel

  • public class FixedHistogramDataModel
extends Object
    This is the fixed data model implementation of the histogram which is created only once when the user executes a node.
    Author:
    Tobias Koetter, University of Konstanz
